---
import LegalLayout from "../layouts/LegalLayout.astro";
import { SUPPORT_EMAIL, LEGAL_ENTITY } from "../config";
---
<LegalLayout lang="en" path="/privacy" title="Privacy Policy">
  <p>Last updated: <strong>[date]</strong>.</p>
  <p>
    This Privacy Policy explains how <strong>Tattoo Inkprep</strong> ("Inkprep", "we")
    processes personal data when you use our mobile app and this website. The data
    controller is <strong>{LEGAL_ENTITY}</strong> (Spain, EU). For any privacy request,
    contact <a href={`mailto:${SUPPORT_EMAIL}`}>{SUPPORT_EMAIL}</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>1. Data we collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Account data:</strong> when you sign in with Google or Apple, we receive your email address and a basic account identifier.</li>
    <li><strong>Designs you upload:</strong> the digital design images you add to a project in order to receive ink recommendations.</li>
    <li><strong>Usage &amp; project data:</strong> the projects you create, your saved palettes, favorites and in-app preferences.</li>
    <li><strong>Subscription data:</strong> your subscription status and purchase identifiers, handled through the app stores and RevenueCat. We never receive or store your full payment-card details.</li>
    <li><strong>Website analytics:</strong> if you consent, anonymous, aggregated usage statistics (see "Cookies &amp; analytics" below).</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>2. Why we use it and legal basis</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>To provide the service</strong> (analyze your designs, return ink recommendations, save your projects): performance of a contract.</li>
    <li><strong>To manage your account and subscription</strong>:performance of a contract.</li>
    <li><strong>To improve and secure the service</strong>:our legitimate interest.</li>
    <li><strong>Website analytics</strong>:your consent.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>3. Processors and third parties</h2>
  <p>We rely on the following providers, who process data on our behalf under data processing agreements:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Supabase</strong>:authentication, database and storage of uploaded design images.</li>
    <li><strong>RevenueCat</strong>:subscription management.</li>
    <li><strong>Apple / Google</strong>:sign-in and payment processing through their stores.</li>
  </ul>
  <p>We do <strong>not</strong> sell your personal data.</p>

  <h2>4. Where your data is stored</h2>
  <p>
    Your account data, project data and uploaded designs are stored on our providers'
    infrastructure. Where data is transferred outside the EU/EEA, it is protected by
    appropriate safeguards (such as the EU Standard Contractual Clauses). <strong>[Confirm storage region/details]</strong>.
  </p>

  <h2>5. Retention</h2>
  <p>
    We keep your account, projects and designs for as long as your account is active.
    When you delete your account (available in the app), your personal data and uploaded
    designs are deleted, except where we must retain limited records to comply with legal
    obligations.
  </p>

  <h2>6. Your rights</h2>
  <p>
    Under the GDPR you have the right to access, rectify, erase, restrict and port your
    data, and to object to certain processing. You can delete your account and associated
    data directly from the app, or by contacting us. You also have the right to lodge a
    complaint with your local supervisory authority (in Spain, the AEPD).
  </p>

  <h2>7. Children</h2>
  <p>Inkprep is a professional tool intended for adults and is not directed to children.</p>

  <h2>8. Cookies &amp; analytics</h2>
  <p>
    This website uses analytics only after you accept it in the consent banner. If you
    decline, no analytics or tracking is loaded. See the banner controls to change your
    choice at any time.
  </p>

  <h2>9. Changes</h2>
  <p>We may update this policy; the "last updated" date above reflects the latest version.</p>

  <h2>10. Contact</h2>
  <p>Data controller: <strong>{LEGAL_ENTITY}</strong>. Email: <a href={`mailto:${SUPPORT_EMAIL}`}>{SUPPORT_EMAIL}</a>.</p>
</LegalLayout>
